        <title>[데이터베이스] N &#43; 1 문제</title>
        <link>https://heetaek.com/p/%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%84%B0%EB%B2%A0%EC%9D%B4%EC%8A%A4-n--1-%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C/</link>
